    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a true automotive masterpiece: a showroom-quality vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This car has been kept in a climate-controlled environment, preserving its deep, mirror-like factory finish with absolutely zero imperfections, swirls, or rock chips. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of luxury; the leather is supple and fragrant, showing no signs of wear, creasing, or fading. Every switch, dial, and electronic component functions with crisp, factory precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, benefiting from a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule fully documented by a comprehensive file of service records. From the pristine engine bay to the spotless undercarriage, this is a collector-grade example that satisfies even the most discerning eye. If you are seeking the finest specimen available on the market, your search ends here.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
