    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person to believe it. It's been pampered since day one and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014honestly, it's in absolutely flawless shape! I\u2019ve loved every mile in it, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy this pristine ride. It drives like a dream, smells brand new, and is ready to hit the road with its next owner. Drop me a message and let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 43900.0,
