    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 997.2 Carrera S, featuring the highly desirable 3.8L naturally aspirated DFI flat-six. This specimen is mechanically flawless, delivering 385 hp through a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle and a factory-optioned limited-slip differential. The chassis is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), providing exceptional lateral stability and damping precision. All service is up-to-date, with a clean DME report showing zero over-revs in higher ranges. From the four-piston aluminum monobloc calipers to the pristine underbody aero-shielding, every component reflects concours-level preservation. A rare opportunity for the purist seeking peak hydraulic steering feel and analog engagement.",
